# Django Matthaios

## Compatibility
This library is designed and tested to work with Django LTS versions:
- Django 4.2.x (e.g., 4.2.20)
- Django 5.2.x (e.g., 5.2.0)

Other versions (e.g., 5.0.x, 5.1.x) are not officially supported. To use this library, ensure your project pins Django to one of these LTS versions in your `pyproject.toml`:

For Django 4.2.x:
```toml
dependencies = ["django>=4.2,<4.3", "django-matthaios>=0.1.0"]
```

## Installation
```bash
pip install django-matthaios
```

Add to INSTALLED_APPS:

```python
INSTALLED_APPS = [
    ...
    'django_matthaios',
]
```

## Admin Panels
`django_matthaios` provides pre-configured admin panels. To disable them, add this to your `settings.py`:

```python
MATTHAIOS_REGISTER_ADMIN = False
```